metadata.name: Mint Pass #1
metadata.description:
This is a collection of Mint Pass for Forza Horizon 5 NFT - combination of top racing game and blockchain.  
Mint Pass holders can burn their Mint Pass and get Forza Horizon 5 NFT for free.  
Mint Free with Mint Pass; get Car Pass & Game Pass and explore vibrant and ever-evolving open world landscapes.
